- and yes, I survived the winter!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">It was always a passion to bring stories to life. From my dolls, to short videos, to most recently, company branding.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">My love for languages have blossomed through my travels and it has given me the opportunity to work in Spanish as well as in English. Puedo hablar y escribir en español sin problema. J\'apprend le français mais je peux faire différentes choses. Along with learning languages, I am certified to teach English and have taught English writing and speaking skills.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">My travels and different homes over the last few years have given me a more open creativity when it comes to writing and visual creations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":16,\"className\":\"desktop-only\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer desktop-only\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Let\'s work together to bring your brand story to life!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\" />\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":16,\"className\":\"desktop-only\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer desktop-only\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"wide\",\"id\":132,\"sizeSlug\":\"la