32px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer desktop-only\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\" />\n<!-- /wp:separator -->','Portfolio','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-12-17 14:52:24','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://local.marinellayule.com/?page_id=194',0,'page','',0),(246,1,'2020-01-13 17:15:00','2020-01-13 17:15:00','<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":32,\"className\":\"desktop-only\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:32px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer desktop-only\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you for dropping by! Here are what some past marketing clients have said about Marinella Yule Marketing Consultant. Read their thoughts on my work in graphics and copy with SEO, work ethic, and communication style. If you like, be sure to check out some of my <strong>podcast interviews at the bottom of the page</strong>! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/7-1024x1024-1.png\",\"id\":980,\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.99\",\"y\":\"0.65\"},\"minHeight\":222} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/7-1024x1024-1.png);background-position:99% 65%;min-height:222px\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>What Marketing Clients Say</strong> <strong>about Marinella</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Graphics and Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Many entrepreneurs are looking for graphics for social media or social media management. I happily to provide those services!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"has-3-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-3-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella is terrific to work with. She understood my requirements&nbsp;and provided <strong>several graphics to meet my social media marketing&nbsp;needs</strong>. I appreciated her feedback and recommendations on how I&nbsp;could improve my social marketing strategy to gain exposure and&nbsp;increase sales.</p><cite>CHANTAL DROUIN-CHARTERS<br><a href=\"https://sharethelovebabybox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">sharethelovebabybox.com</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>For a professional, great follow up, and on-time delivery of&nbsp;service, I highly recommend Marinella. She was a <strong>great help in&nbsp;designing some graphics, in different languages</strong>, for my&nbsp;immigration business Ad campaign. She was able to understand&nbsp;the concept of the business and design accordingly.</p><p></p><cite>RIHAM AL BAKOUNI, RCIC <br><a href=\"https://bakouni-consulting.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">bakouni-consulting.ca</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella’s <strong>output of completed social media projects has exceeded my expectations</strong> for the position as well as&nbsp;surpassed&nbsp;the corporate social media account’s&nbsp;production.&nbsp;She was posting multiple posts and increased our followers significantly.</p><cite>ALLAN WILAYTO, REGIONAL SALES DIRECTOR – GDT NORTHEAST</cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Creativity, SEO, and Written Edits</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Graphics and written copy need creativity to stand out, but I don\'t forget the SEO! With my experience in teaching English, I am able to make sure errors are minimized or completely avoided. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>I had the best experience working with Marinella! I hired her to create some social media graphics for a new brand I was launching. <strong>She was really prepared with creative ideas and impressed me by how quick&nbsp;she delivered me high quality graphics!</strong> I loved what she created and I would highly recommend her for anyone who is looking for a graphic designer!&nbsp;</p><cite>MIKAH SULLIVAN<strong>,<br></strong><a href=\"http://lostabbey.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">The Lost Abbey Brewery</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella helped me develop and troubleshoot a new website and&nbsp;also gave me excellent SEO recommendations. <strong>She was extremely professional and knowledgeable and answered all of my questions&nbsp;patiently.</strong> I recommend working with her. Thank you for your help&nbsp;Marinella!</p><cite>NOA YAAKOBA-ZOHAR,<br><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/noayaakobazohar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MSc student in Human Nutrition</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><strong>Marinella\'s editing work on my project was impeccable.</strong> Despite the scientific vocabulary that comes out of her area of expertise, she knew how to help me formulate my ideas in a clear and professional manner. She exceeded my expectations and the quality of her work is exceptional. I will definitely recommend her in the future. Since English is not my first language, her input was more than helpful. Thank you so much, Marinella!</p><cite>MELISSA BEAUDOIN,<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.thesilentvoicesproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\">PH</a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/melissabeaudoin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">.D Candidate</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Marketing Strategy and Communications</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Sometimes entrepreneurs need a game plan and others need an open flow of communication with the consultant and with their target market. It is my privilege to provide both!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"has-3-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-3-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella is very intuitive in creating marketing that works. <strong>She was able to create posts for Pinterest for me, something that I have never thought to use for my business.</strong> She came up with graphics that I can easily use to promote my business. She is excited and able to come up with brilliant ideas in a very short time. I have worked with others that need constant check ins. I am busy and don’t have time for that. Marinella was able to give me exactly what I wanted. <strong>She is a dream</strong>.</p><cite>ANNA MILNE, <br><a href=\"https://annamilne.mapleorganics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">annamilne.mapleorganics.com</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella helped me immensely in marketing my business. <strong>She absolutely goes above and beyond</strong>! <strong>She is a great communicator, very easy to work with and works quickly to complete the job at hand.</strong> I highly recommend Marinella and will definitely continue using her to grow my business. Thank you Marinella!</p><cite>JENNIFER JACOBS, <br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.smartypantstutoring.ca/\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://www.smartypantstutoring.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">smartypantstutoring.ca</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella’s services exceeded my expectations. <strong>She created a number of beautiful graphics for my business social media posts alongside&nbsp;with copies for them that are engaging&nbsp;and spark conversations</strong>. Marinella took time to understand what I was looking for and her delivery was very timely. I would recommend her services to anyone looking to outsource&nbsp;their digital marketing&nbsp;or even get some help and save time. Thank you Marinella for your amazing graphics!</p><cite>MAGGIE PEROTIN,<br><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/BusinesswomenWithPassion4Life/\"></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/BusinesswomenWithPassion4Life/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">BusinesswomenWithPassion4Life</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Marketing Plans and Work Ethic</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">I am excited to help you build and grow your business through marketing plans and timely responses and deliveries of assets.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><strong>Amazing marketing skills, efficient, on point, on time, on target and&nbsp;easy to communicate.</strong> I will recommend Marinella 100% She is a&nbsp;team player and a professional in all she does. Ever since she took&nbsp;over the sanctuary page traffic increased. Thanks a million for you&nbsp;valuable work.</p><cite>SANDRA CLINE,<br><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandra-cline-853a846a/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Mountain High Animal Sanctuary Coordinator</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Thank you so much for your help. We covered a lot of great information and created some amazing marketing ideas for my membership. <strong>Thank you so much for the marketing plan.</strong> I love the way it’s designed and the detailed steps for me to take.&nbsp;</p><cite>SHAY RAMSEE,<br>Events by Shay</cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella is prompt and very professional. She was also very&nbsp;patient with my timeline. I recommend working with her 100%. <strong>She&nbsp;won\'t stop until you\'re happy with the output!</strong> Thank you,&nbsp;Marinella!</p><cite>NINA REYNOLDS,<br><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ninagreynolds/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Pretty Neat Solutions Owner</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Persistent, Determined, and Outside the Box</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">My travel experience has taught me to be persistent when making plans, determined to see the world, and live a life outside the box. I bring all this to help you with marketing and building and growing your business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"has-3-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-3-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Wow, just wow! I explained my vision to Marinella to have a lounge for my affiliates where there was an abundance of social media posts and copy they could use to sell my online course Boundary Essentials for Empaths. <strong>With just that, she scanned through the course and created a beautiful set of Instagram, Facebook and Pinterest posts along with copy for every single post!</strong> Marinella was quick, creative, communicated well and created designs that were in alignment with my branding. I will absolutely be using her services again in the future and will recommend her to other busy biz owners in my industry.</p><cite>BREE SUTTON,<br><a href=\"https://intuitiflow.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Intuitiflow.com</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella has been absolutely wonderful to work with! <strong>She replied to every single one of my messages in a very timely manner, shared some great ideas on how to market my business better, provided graphics that turned out beautifully, and was very professional</strong>. I would highly recommend working with Marinella!!</p><cite>KRISTY JUDD,<br><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LushLeafDesigns/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Lush Leaf Design</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>I had the pleasure of having Marinella work on my companies website. I am not a creative writer, I needed help! <strong>Marinella stepped up and ran with what I gave her and she did so quickly and the communication was beyond what I could have ever expected</strong>. She did what I asked and more. Thank you Again Marinella!</p><cite>CHANTAL LEBLANC<br><a href=\"https://devanter.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Devanter Bookkeeping &amp; Office Solutions Inc.</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Awesome! Thanks so much for your help! I really appreciate your expertise, and <strong>have noticed already how [the website] has climbed up the Google ladder</strong>!  My client, the owner, has been noticing too and is very pleased.</p><p></p><cite>DORALIN GINTER, <a href=\"http://dginspired.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">dginspired.com</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Details are Important</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Within everything, the saying is: \"the devil is in the details.\" This is either in regards to SEO and keywords or with a simple note. Details are important for our relationship as well as for every project. Together, we can reach your marketing goals. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"has-3-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-3-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella is very professional, detailed, and prompt when&nbsp;completing projects for me. <strong>She is always going above and beyond&nbsp;on her work delivery </strong>and is such an asset to have at our agency!</p><cite>ANGELICA BROOKS,<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.thesilentvoicesproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://www.thesilentvoicesproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">The Silent Voices Project</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><strong>Marinella was extremely helpful when it came to improving my SEO</strong>. She was able to explain in detail what I needed to add and/or improve. She went over meta tags, key words, backlinks and much more! I highly recommend Marinella for any SEO needs you may have.</p><cite>Karly Whitaker<br><a href=\"http://hourglassvirtualassisting.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hourglass Virtual Assisting</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Marinella gave me some great advice on how to improve my&nbsp;Facebook page and drive users to my website. <strong>She followed up&nbsp;with me in a timely way, and answered my questions in a clear&nbsp;concise way</strong>- it was a pleasure dealing with her.</p><p></p><cite>AVIVA ABRAHAMS,<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Aviva-Abraham-Creative-Planning-Financial-Group-324123867685731/\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Aviva-Abraham-Creative-Planning-Financial-Group-324123867685731/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Creative Planning Financial Group</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":32,\"className\":\"desktop-only\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:32px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer desktop-only\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stock-by-Jewels-FREE-0034-scaled.jpg\",\"id\":979,\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.33\",\"y\":\"0.60\"},\"minHeight\":331} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stock-by-Jewels-FREE-0034-scaled.jpg);background-position:33% 60%;min-height:331px\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__i