/p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Again, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/the-art-of-customer-service/\" target=\"_blank\">we don’t want to burn bridges</a>. You never know where or when that person will cross our path again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I hope these little insights will help you either formulating the best rejection letter possible and how to accept the letter if you are to receive one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would like help writing professional documents such as a form letter or other copywriting needs, feel free to shoot me an email!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons aligncenter\"><!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-outline\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/contact/\">Contact</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How to Send a Rejection Letter Professionally','Learn how to make your rejection letter as professional and polite as possible in order to not burn bridges with other entrepreneurs in your industry. ','inherit','closed','closed','','805-revision-v1','','','2020-06-20 21:13:18','2020-06-20 21:13:18','',805,'http://local.marinellayule.com/805-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(810,1,'2020-06-20 21:14:28','2020-06-20 21:14:28','<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"https://a8ctm1.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/adventure-calm-clouds-1.jpg\",\"id\":648,\"dimRatio\":20,\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim-20 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(https://a8ctm1.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/adventure-calm-clouds-1.jpg)\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__i