ategy and implementation!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:button {\"textColor\":\"background\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-outline\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button aligncenter is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background-color\">Contact</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":96} -->\n<div style=\"height:96px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->','','','inherit','closed','closed','','422-revision-v1','','','2020-09-15 18:54:31','2020-09-15 18:54:31','',422,'http://local.marinellayule.com/422-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(956,1,'2020-09-15 19:02:06','2020-09-15 19:02:06','','Stock by Jewels FREE - 0006','','inherit','open','closed','','stock-by-jewels-free-0006','','','2020-09-15 19:02:48','2020-09-15 19:02:48','',374,'http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stock-by-Jewels-FREE-0006.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(957,1,'2020-09-15 19:05:16','2020-09-15 19:05:16','<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Marinella Yule provides a wide range of services and different needs can be combined together into one comprehensive package to help build and grow your business!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not sure what you need? Check out these items and let\'s chat more on creating a custom package for your needs!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":32} -->\n<div style=\"height:32px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Stock-by-Jewels-FREE-0002-scaled.jpg\"