and how to be efficient in my content creation, now I would be creating a content calendar for them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This step is more after the contract is signed, but I would have a list of ideas that I would want to discuss with them in order to formally establish a content calendar.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once this step is complete, then it would be actually creating the content!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I hope this article helped you in understanding the social media strategy process and some thought processes a marketer goes through in preparation for a complimentary call or before they market your business. Feel free to schedule your <a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/contact/\">complimentary discovery call</a> with me to jump start your marketing or social media strategy! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Or be sure to keep an eye out for the <strong>Build a Business eCourse</strong> that will help you conquer your business goals! The course will dive into the different aspects of building your business online from target markets to building a website to SEO to marketing. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Steps in Creating a Social Media Strategy','','inherit','closed','closed','','1015-revision-v1','','','2020-09-23 18:27:53','2020-09-23 18:27:53','',1015,'http://local.marinellayule.com/1015-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1018,1,'2020-09-23 18:29:46','2020-09-23 18:29:46','','20','','inherit','open','closed','','20','','','2020-10-01 14:04:47','2020-10-01 14:04:47','',1015,'http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1019,1,'2020-09-23 18:30:03','2020-09-23 18:30:03','','21','','inherit','open','closed','','21','','','2020-09-23 18:30:22','2020-09-23 18:30:22','',1015,'ht