s a course online. Courses can cover a variety of information from history to math to marketing. They can also be a variety of prices. Some can be hundreds of dollars and others can be free.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/build-a-business-ecourse-2/\">Build a Business eCourse</a> covers all the items you need to get started creating your business online. From my own online business journey and talking with my own clients who are starting out, I realized there was a need for budget friendly or do-it-yourself course out there for new online entrepreneurs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many of the eCourses out there are very specialized in certain information such as one course just on social media marketing. One course just on social media content creation. One course on coding.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It can be tiring for entrepreneurs to keep buying different courses from different sources. Wouldn’t it be better to buy from one shop?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some ways that Build a Business eCourse is different and will help you succeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about Pricing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A lot of business eCourses really focus on marketing and design. Many don’t talk about how to price yourself, how to invoice, and all the other information on numbers. Build a Business jumps into these details and goes over different ways in order for you to pick the best way for you!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about Networking</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Surprisingly, networking has been one of my top questions from clients and other business professionals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/in-person-and-online-networking/\">“How do you network?”</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This question comes up a lot either in how to start a conversation or how to network during COVID or online times.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business offers a chapter focused on these questions! A big part of starting a business is networking and building a professional network. You can start this at any time, even before you have your website up!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about some Coding</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business is not a coding eCourse. If you are looking for a straight up coding course, this isn’t it. However, Build a Business does cover basic coding information and vocabulary. When building or maintaining your website you might find yourself needing some basic coding. This chapter covers basic coding vocabulary and how to read the code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about SEO</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new online entrepreneur, it is never to early to start learning and implementing SEO. Even starting your website, you need to think about SEO because going back and updating it can be a hassle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This chapter dives into SEO vocabulary and where you can start implementing and free tools you can use to make your online presence stand out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Buy ALL or Buy separately, have for a lifetime</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business offers multiple chapters under one course. This means that you can buy each chapter separately. If you just want the SEO and Networking chapter, you can buy just those. If you don’t want the Branding chapter, you are not required to pay for it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the reverse, if you do want to buy all the chapters, you get a discount on the full package!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Plus, you get to keep the information for a lifetime!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Each chapter has written and video material for learners of all types</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business provides materials for all types of learners. Are you more of a reader? We have worksheets. Are you more of a listener or like watching how it is done? We have videos!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1124,\"width\":517,\"height\":517,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/40-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"How Build a Business eCourse is different\" class=\"wp-image-1124\" width=\"517\" height=\"517\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interested in learning more about Build a Business eCourse? Check out more information on this <a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/build-a-business-ecourse-2/\">page</a>. If you have follow up questions, be sure to <a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/contact/\">email Marinella</a> at <a href=\"mailto:myopenpassport@gmail.com\">myopenpassport@gmail.com</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How Build a Business eCourse is Different','Learn how Build a Business eCourse is different from the other business eCourse and how you can start building today with Marinella Yule.','future','open','open','','build-a-business-ecourse-differences','','','2020-10-01 15:46:50','2020-10-01 15:46:50','',0,'http://local.marinellayule.com/?p=1060',0,'post','',0),(1061,1,'2020-09-23 21:51:29','2020-09-23 21:51:29','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First, what is an e-Course? An e-Course is a course online. Courses can cover a variety of information from history to math to marketing. They can also be a variety of prices. Some can be hund