lly when it comes to business and entrepreneurship, this course is also for you! We cover a variety of topics including some of the confusing website platforms and hosting, SEO, and invoicing programs.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This course doesn’t just cover social media!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. An Experienced and Trained Host</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are looking for a course that is ran by someone who has the experience and training then Build a Business e-Course is for you! This course was created by Marinella Yule who studied marketing in university and then proceeded to work in a variety of places including USA, Europe, and Canada.&nbsp; She incorporates her own experience and her observations of other entrepreneurs in order to make sure your business is built firmly!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>YES! FOR YOU!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If all of the above resonated with you then yes! This course is for you! Click here to learn more or if you have any follow up questions about Build a Business and or your host, Marinella, feel free to send an email to <a href=\"mailto:myopenpassport@gmail.com\">myopenpassport@gmail.com</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Is Build a Business E-Course for You?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1062-revision-v1','','','2020-09-23 21:51:49','2020-09-23 21:51:49','',1062,'http://local.marinellayule.com/1062-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1064,1,'2020-09-23 22:03:16','2020-09-23 22:03:16','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What is the difference between hiring someone vs paying for an eCourse? From the outset the answer might be very obvious, but there might be some other items you haven’t thought of.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In regards to Build a Business eCourse, this is a great place to get started for building your business as it will give you information that could help you hire the right person.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Hiring Someone for the Work</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>1. They will do it for you (you give up control)</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first thought when it comes to hiring someone is that they will do the work for you. However, the opposite viewpoint for this is that you give up control. Often, this means you have to give your passwords to your accounts to the person or you have to trust their abilities to create your vision.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>2. They have more training and experience (or not)</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The benefit to hiring someone is that they have more training and experience in that particular area. Or, at least, you believe they do. One of the downsides of hiring someone is that in fact they don’t have the actual training and experience, which could cost you a lot more time and money than previously planned.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>3. Hiring Someone Could Cost Hundreds of Dollars</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hiring someone, especially if they are highly trained and experienced, can cost you hundreds, if not, thousands of dollars depending on the particular job.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>4. You have to explain what you are looking for when Hiring Someone</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The biggest downside of hiring someone vs an ecourse is that, they can’t read your mind, unfortunately. You have to explain what you are looking for. Perhaps you don’t know what you are looking for, but you know it when you see it or rather you know what you don’t want when you see it. This thought process is completely normal, but it can be costly for your time (and theirs) and your money.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pay for an eCourse</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>1. Saves money</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The major benefit of doing an eCourse vs hiring someone is that it saves you money. You get a lot more information for a lot less and Build a Business also gives you information on the different programs you can use and HOW you use them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>2. An eCourse gives information on all aspects</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business eCourse goes through all the different steps of building a business online from figuring out your target market to how to price yourself to even how to network! It really does cover everything under the sun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>3. You have control over your baby</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let’s be honest. Our business is our baby. We have a vision for its growth. There might be a special meaning involved in your business for you. By doing an eCourse and doing the different steps yourself, you won’t have to relinquish control over your baby to someone else. You will have full control over the reigns.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>4. You know what you want (or don’t want)</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Precisely what is mentioned above, sometimes you might not know what you want or you might only know what you DON’T want. This is totally normal. But, as mentioned above, hiring an external person is just that: an external person. They won’t be able to read your mind.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Going through Build a Business eCourse enables you to either create what is in your mind and vision yourself OR, after this course, you will have the ability to further explain your vision to that external person, which will cut down on time and, potentially, money.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interested in learning more about Build a Business eCourse? Check out more information on this page. If you have follow up questions, be sure to <a href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/contact/\">email Marinella</a> at <a href=\"mailto:myopenpassport@gmail.com\">myopenpassport@gmail.com</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Hiring Someone vs an eCourse','','inherit','closed','closed','','1056-revision-v1','','','2020-09-23 22:03:16','2020-09-23 22:03:16','',1056,'http://local.marinellayule.com/1056-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1065,1,'2020-09-23 22:04:44','2020-09-23 22:04:44','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business eCourse is releasing soon! What is it? Build a Business eCourse is your comprehensive e-Course that covers all the steps in building a business online from branding to SEO to setting up your website and more!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now that COVID has halted in person businesses and forced many to stay at home, you might be thinking now is the time to start your own business either as a full time job or as a side gig.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Either way, don’t jump in without knowing the different parts of making a successful business!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You might be asking yourself why you need this particular eCourse. There are so many out there. Why this one?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some reasons why you need Build a Business eCourse.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Saves Hundreds of Dollars</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are hiring someone to help you set up your business online by either doing everything or just creating a website, this could cost hundreds even thousands of dollars. AND, it could even cost you much of your time coordinating with the person and discussing the different steps of the process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some other e-courses cost hundreds of dollars for one piece of information that is covered in Build a Business. Or, sometimes a course holds way more information than what you need and you end up paying for things that are not needed for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business ecourse is a budget friendly e-course that goes through all the steps of setting up your business online from branding to SEO to setting up your website and more! You also get to pick and choose which chapters you want to purchase or you can purchase the whole course.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Get Inside Knowledge</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business e-course was created with the expertise of a marketing professional. Marinella Yule graduated from university with a marketing degree and proceeded to work in marketing in a variety of places including the US, Europe, and Canada.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Know the Info Beforehand</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If or when you do decide to hire external help, don’t go into the deal blind. Having a basic understanding of branding, SEO, marketing in general, etc will help you discuss with the person you might hire about the project. You will be able to better convey what you are looking for or ask better questions to make sure this individual is who you want to hire!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Save Time Researching Tools</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As the saying goes, “time is money.” Finding the proper tools to help you start your business and or working in your business can be a hassle. We have done the research for you and give you videos on how to work the different programs so you don’t have to try them to see if they would be a good fit for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On top of researching the different programs, we make sure to tell you the ones that also offer a free account! Perfect for budget friendly entrepreneurs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Save Time Learning the Tools</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Just like the above point, we provide videos in this e-course that gives you a brief introduction to the different programs on how to start working directly. we also provide tips and tricks to make working in the program easier and more efficient.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Discount on one on one workings with Marinella</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The bonus! If you decide to purchase one chapter, multiple chapters, or the whole course, you will receive a discount on one on one meetings with Marinella on marketing, if you wish!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interested in learning more about Build a Business e-course? Check out more information on this page. If you have follow up questions, be sure to email Marinella at <a href=\"mailto:myopenpassport@gmail.com\">myopenpassport@gmail.com</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Reasons why you need Build a Business eCourse','','inherit','closed','closed','','1058-revision-v1','','','2020-09-23 22:04:44','2020-09-23 22:04:44','',1058,'http://local.marinellayule.com/1058-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1066,1,'2020-09-23 22:05:48','2020-09-23 22:05:48','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First, what is an e-Course? An e-Course is a course online. Courses can cover a variety of information from history to math to marketing. They can also be a variety of prices. Some can be hundreds of dollars and others can be free.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business e-Course covers all the items you need to get started creating your business online. From my own online business journey and talking with my own clients who are starting out, I realized there was a need for budget friendly or do-it-yourself course out there for new online entrepreneurs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many of the e-Courses out there are very specialized in certain information such as one course just on social media marketing. One course just on social media content creation. One course on coding.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It can be tiring for entrepreneurs to keep buying different courses from different sources. Wouldn’t it be better to buy from one shop?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some ways that Build a Business e-Course is different and will help you succeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about Pricing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A lot of business e-Courses really focus on marketing and design. Many don’t talk about how to price yourself, how to invoice, and all the other information on numbers. Build a Business jumps into these details and goes over different ways in order for you to pick the best way for you!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about Networking</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Surprisingly, networking has been one of my top questions from clients and other business professionals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“How do you network?”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This question comes up a lot either in how to start a conversation or how to network during COVID or online times.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business offers a chapter focused on these questions! A big part of starting a business is networking and building a professional network. You can start this at any time, even before you have your website up!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about some Coding</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business is not a coding e-Course. If you are looking for a straight up coding course, this isn’t it. However, Build a Business does cover basic coding information and vocabulary. When building or maintaining your website you might find yourself needing some basic coding. This chapter covers basic coding vocabulary and how to read the code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Talks about SEO</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new online entrepreneur, it is never to early to start learning and implementing SEO. Even starting your website, you need to think about SEO because going back and updating it can be a hassle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This chapter dives into SEO vocabulary and where you can start implementing and free tools you can use to make your online presence stand out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Buy ALL or Buy separately, have for a lifetime</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Build a Business offers multiple chapters under one course. This means that you can buy each chapter separately. If you just want the SEO and Networking chapter, you can buy just those. If you don’t want the Branding chapter, you are not required to pay for it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the reverse, if you do want to buy all the chapters, you get a discount on the full package!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Plus, you get to keep the information for a lifetime!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n