dollars for a service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As the saying goes, give a man a fish, he eats for a day, teach the man how to fish, he eats for life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, grab your fishing pole because that\'s what we are talking about here!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An eCourse to help entrepreneurs just like you build their business!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":20} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would like to learn how to become a beta tester, contact Marinella today!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:button {\"backgroundColor\":\"primary\",\"textColor\":\"background\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-default\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-primary-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"http://local.marinellayule.com/contact/\">Get in Touch</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":32} -->\n<div style=\"height:32px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/24.jpg\",\"id\":1026,\"dimRatio\":100,\"customOverlayColor\":\"#495859\",\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.46\",\"y\":\"0.08\"},\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/24.jpg);background-color:#495859;background-position:46% 8%\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Here is what Build a Business eCourse covers:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Branding and Target Market Visualization</li><li>How to Do Your Own Branding</li><li>Information on Different Websites and Website Hosting</li><li>How to Build Your Own Website</li><li>Basic Coding Information for Website Tweaks</li><li>Free Tools You Can Use for Marketing Projects</li><li>Competitor Research</li><li>SEO: All you need to know</li><li>Plugins for Your Website to Make it Run Even Better</li><li>Further Marketing Ideas and Content Creations</li><li>Bookkeeping Tips and Tricks</li><li>Invoicing and Contracts</li><li>Networking and Building Relationships for Your Business </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is your one stop shop for all your building needs. I give you the Legos and the rest is up to you! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/event-countdown {\"eventDate\":\"2020-11-01T15:53:00\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-event-countdown\"><div class=\"event-countdown__date\">2020-11-01T15:53:00</div><div class=\"event-countdown__counter\"><p><strong class=\"event-countdown__day\">&nbsp;</strong> days</p><p><span><strong class=\"event-countdown__hour\">&nbsp;</strong> hours</span><span><strong class=\"event-countdown__minute\">&nbsp;</strong> minutes</span><span><strong class=\"event-countdown__second\">&nbsp;</strong> seconds</span></p><p>until</p></div><div class=\"event-countdown__event-title\"><p>Launch of Build a Business eCourse</p></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:jetpack/event-countdown -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/24.jpg\",\"id\":1026,\"dimRatio\":80,\"customOverlayColor\":\"#495859\",\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.46\",\"y\":\"0.08\"},\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim-80 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://local.marinellayule.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/24.jpg);background-color:#495859;background-position:46% 8%\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textCo